r customers’ friendships and successes have significantly contributed to our own success. Numerous farms and families that we’ve had the privilege of getting started have done very well with their own breeding programs. It is equally exciting for us to see the progeny of these programs stand as Champion show winners and creating successful businesses! Notably, our program is different from most others in the industry today, as we have extensive end-use expertise in converting raw fleece into beautiful fashionable apparel. This fleece to fashion program has specialized in breeding distinct color lines as well as an elite fine-fiber line.','609-397-2212','woodsedgeevents@aol.com','Linda Berry Walker','','Weekend from April through December, 10:00 a.m. till 4:00 p.m.','','http://www.woodsedge.com/','','78 Bowne Station Road','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed1ec7f1-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','08559 ','Hay Rides, Farm Tours, Visual Zoo (non-petting), Others:WoodsEdge Country Botique featuring alpaca & suri llama products','Private Parties, Weddings and Receptions, Corporate Events, Host Fundraisers/Events','','2012-02-29 15:17:15','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7657cf2f-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Tomenchok Farms','Tomenchok Farms is a family operated farm specializing in organically raised gourmet poultry, pork, eggs, vegetables, and fruit. We work in conjunction with Podere DiMelo just down the road.','(609) 397-7845','Rob@AlliedElectronics.com','Robert Tomenchok','','Evenings and Weekends by appointment','','http://www.tomenchokfarms.com/','','145 Rocktown-Lambertville Road','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed1ec7f1-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','08530','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:15','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('765ba430-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Podere di Melo Farm','Podere di Melo (\'Apple Tree Farm\' in Italian) is a family run Certified Naturally Grown farm that specializes in food of the Italian and French countryside. We raise Italian and French varieites of vegetables (including San Marzano tomatoes), slow-growing, French-style poultry, heritage pork, duck, meat rabbits, honey, and farm fresh eggs. All our animals raised on fresh, chemical free pastures. We never use synthetic herbicides, pesticides, antibiotics or added hormones. Together with our partner farm - Tomenchock Farms - we are your local source in Hunterdon County for Italian and French food. Many of our meats can be reserved online. Visit us today at www.poderedimelo.com.','609-397-9788','info@poderedimelo.com','David Hauser','','Weekends and by appointment','','http://www.poderedimelo.com/','','264 Rocktown-Lambertville Rd','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed1ec7f1-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','08530','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:15','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('765f7982-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','North Slope Farm','North Slope Farm is a 55 acre diversified organic farm, located in central New Jersey. Our crops include vegetables, flowers, small fruits and small livestock. We serve a variety of markets including our retail farmstand, and off site farmers markets as well as special wholesale clients. Primary tilage and cultivation is done with the use of both tractors and hand tools. While we strive to improve efficiency and mechanixation of crop care, the procudtion crew remains the most valuable aspect. Training opportunities available. www.northslopefarm.com','(609) 466-8330','northslopefarm@comcast.net','M. Rassweiler','','Months of operation: April through November The farm is open Wednesday noon to dusk April through November','','http://www.northslopefarm.com/','','386 Rock Rd. East','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed1ec7f1-