we are always listening to our customers we now carry clover, alfalfa, buckwheat, tupelo and orange blossom honeys. In addition we are licensed from the New Jersey Department of Agriculture to use the Jersey Fresh logo on our New Jersey products. It helps that Mary comes from a family in which her father was a hobbyist and commercial beekeeper in Maryland and Georgia. In addition while she was working at the Beltsville Agricultural Research Center in Beltsville, Maryland, Mary began working with bees. Mary carries on that tradition and then some since she now runs the beeswax side of E&M Gold Beekeepers which includes creating formal beeswax candles, beeswax figurine candles, beeswax plaques and beeswax hand creams and lip balms. We are active members of the New Jersey Beekeepers Association (NJBA), the Central Jersey Beekeepers Association (CJBA), the American Honey Producers Association (AHPA), the Northeast Organic Farming Association (NOFA), and the National Honey Board (NHB). In addition we subscribe to industry journals, Bee Culture and The American Beekeeping Journal. We presently hold the following positions in the Central Jersey Beekeepers Association: County Fair Chairwoman, and Recertification Chairman. In addition we give educational talks and presentations at schools, associations and county fairs.','(732)542-6528','emgold.beekeepers@verizon.net','Mary  Kosenski','','','','http://www.emgoldbeekeepers.com/','','113 Hope Rd.','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed1ec7f1-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','07724','Others:Visit Apiary- please call to make reservation','Others:Small tours of the Apiary & Honey House - please call to make reservation','','2012-02-29 15:17:16','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('76e7c643-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Sickles Market','Sickles, The Fresh Market, is committed to providing our customers with a unique blend of the highest qual