ms we know how important it is for you to know where your food comes from. All produce found at Southside is raised by us right here on our farm and picked fresh daily. Come visit our farm where you can injoy fresh, healthy fruits and vegetables and meet \"Your Farmer\". ','252-946-2487 ','info@southsidefarms.com ','Shawn & Tracey Harding','','7am-6pm Monday - Saturday. Open April - July','','www.southsidefarms.com ','','320 Harding Lane ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27817 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:25','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7c212707-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Ann Marie\'s Cakes  ','Susan has been a Professional Cake Decorator for over 5 years in Wilmington NC. She started her business to give her customers affordable custom speciality cakes. We recently relocated to Beaufort County.   We also make Chocolate covered Pretzels and Cherries, Oversized Cookies and Brownies, and any custom candy or Dessert you may need.   We offer custom Coastal and Beach Scene cakes, Graduation and Sweet Sixteen Cakes, Shower and Wedding Cakes. ','252-944-6598 ','annmariescakes@gmail.com ','Susan & Brandi Bartelt','','Call us any time, or Email annmariescakes@gmail.com ','','','','438 kirby Grange Ave. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27808 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:25','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7c2240ff-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Landscaping Unlimited, Inc.','We,Buddy & Nancy Brickhouse started this business together in 1984. We are still a family owned business but have grown quite a bit in the last 26 years. We are fully insured and license for the landscape and maintenance industry. We have to sons which plan to take over our business after they complete their business d