 freely on pasture that has not been sprayed or treated with poisons for over 30 years. In keeping with a humane care tradition, those animals that require antibiotics for a specific medical condition receive them, but are not used in our beef sales.   Or beef is grain finished. We use as much of our own organic grain as possible. What we can\'t provide ourselves, we buy from our neighbor. Though not an organic product, its as local as you can get. We believe in stewardship of the land ... we take care of the land, and the land will take care of us. ','919-742-4433 ','murrayswife@aol.com ','Esta Cohen','','Open everyday, just call ahead to make sure we\'re here. ','','www.cohenfarm.com ','','688 Van Thomas Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27312 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d1d3578-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Costa Quarter Horses  ','Costa Quarter Horses has been involved in reining for 20 years. We have been breeding reining quarter horses for the last 15 years. We take pride in breeding fountain blood lines.    Our babies are King blood and Tanquery Gin who is also Continal King blood. Babies are bred mainly for reining but also could be used for cutting and working cowhorse. They are very physical.    We are a small breeder so our babies are handled daily,are good minded and well taked care of here. ','919.837.2154 ','costaquarterhorses@rtelco.net ','Tony & Rita Costa','','By appointment only ','','www.dreamhorse.com ','','1111 NC Hwy 42 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27252 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d1e2ac1-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Eagle Springs Farm  ','','919-545-9919 ','Michelle@Eaglesprin