 We also wholesale some of our fruits to some grocery chains.    We also sell many products from Dutch Valley, an Amish food company which specializes in wholesome, fresh food items. We also stock South Mountain meat and cheese products.    We have pick-your-own in all of our fruit crops, except peaches, and some of our vegetable crops. Request a \"Crop List\" to check on availability. ','','fruitgrower@netzero.net ','Ervin or Debbie Lineberger','','April hours: 8am-6pm weekdays, 8am-2pm Saturdays, May hours: 7:30am-7pm weekdays, 7:30am-5pm Saturdays and 1-5pm Sundays ','','','','300 Goforth Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28086','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d5b1127-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Proffitt Family Farms','Our mission is to produce high quality beef grown in a natural way. To provide our animals with an environment that lets them live their entire lives as nature intended, by allowing them to forage exclusively on pasture. On our farm we let the cows and pasture land sustain each other with only rain and sunshine. Our animals are never given hormones or antibiotics. We are an Animal Welfare Approved farm which is a strict certification program that assures our customers when we say our animals are the best treated cattle in the land. Come see for yourself - we welcome visitors anytime to our farm, just call Shelley at 704-751-6455 to schedule your visit.    Only 100% Grass fed and Finished beef can give all the health benefits plus all the tenderness and taste you deserve. Check out the nutrition page on our website to read about all the incredible health benefits our beef provides. Decide for yourself and then you will most likely never purchase store bought beef from grain fed animals again.   We sell our beef from our farms store here in Kings Mountain, plus we are at 