d miss ice cream, fresh baked goods and canned goods are just some of what to expect. ALL WELCOME, COME ONE AND ALL AND BRING YOUR FRIENDS. ','(704)538-8661,(704)472-9668 ','elliottsupply@carolina.rr.com ','Hilda,Bob,Mark','','This years Heritage Days Antique Tractor and Engine Show will take place October 1st and 2nd, 2011, Gates open to the public at 10am, Prices for the event are $5 at the gate; 12 and younger are free. ','','','','5022 Brooks Chapel Rd (PO Box 225) ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28136 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d630bbe-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Great Pyrenees Of South Mountain  ','We first started out by raising Llamas and the went to Boer Goats that we raised for about four years. We bought our first Pyrenees to guard our goats and fell in love with the breed. That one Pyr. turned into eight. We have since quit raising Boer goats and concentrate solely on our dogs. Give us a call or just drop by to see us, we\'d love to meet you. ','704-538-9160 ','PYRENEES8@carolina.rr.com','Rhonda Barrett','','Anytime. ','','www.angelfire.com/pe2/pyrenees/index.html ','','112 Navaho Drive ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28020 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6437ea-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','HarvestWorks, Inc. ','HarvestWorks, Inc. is a farm-based non-profit organization. We offer an array of public services as described in our products section. Our mission is to provide employment opportunities and direct care services to individuals with developmental disabilities.   Located in Shelby, NC, we invite you to visit or gift shop, petting zoo, ride our tram, and complete crafts with our participants. HarvestWorks also has a mobile petting zoo, a restaurant where we serve lunch monday through friday and catering services are available.   Join our mailing list at www.HarvestWorksInc.org to be updated about special events. ','704-487-7777 ','jadams@cvii.org ','Jeff Adams','','Gift Store: Monday - Saturday 8 am to 5 pm Petting Zoo: call for a tour or visit our website to see when we\'re having events Administrative Offices: Mon. - Fri. 8:00 am to 4:00 pm Group Tours scheduled by appointment ','','www.harvestworksinc.org ','','891 North Post Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28150','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6514b2-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Jerry\'s Nut Company  ','We deep fried red skin peanuts in the shell, offering four flavors, Salted, Cajun, Chipolte BBQ,Extra Hot Cajun, Habanera, and Salt and Vinegar.   Please inquire about Retail and Wholesale opportunities.   They make great fundraisers. We offer special pricing. ','704-538-0996 ','jerrysilver@shelby.net ','Jerry Silver','','5:30am-10:00pm Mon-Sat 7:00am-10:00pm Sun ','','jerrysnuts.com ','','4400 Polkville Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28136 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d666562-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Lineberger\'s Killdeer Farm  ','We\'ve been farming at Killdeer Farm for the past 22 years, growing a variety of fruits and vegetables. These are all picked fresh daily and sold in our indoor Farm Market located on-site, along with other local produce. In addition, we sell our own jams, jellies and honey; South Mtn products, a large selection of Amish products, fruit juices, fruity slushies, etc. You may also pick-your-own fruit (except peaches) and some vegetables (during certain harvest times).   Some of our fruit crops are packaged and delivered wholesale through local grocery chains. When in season, look for \"Lineberger\'s\" BLACKBERRIES and MUSCADINES in your grocery\'s produce section.   We are a family operation. We have six children (with paying jobs) and eight grandchildren. Since our harvest season is labor intensive, we no longer have field trips/scheduled tours; however, we hope you\'ll visit us, browse thru the market, possibly pick-your-own fruit, and take a break at the picnic tables while you grab a snack and a fresh, fruity slushie. For more info, call to request a copy of our current \"Crop List\" and to get on our e-mailing list. ','704-739-6602 ','fruitgrower@netzero.net ','Ervin or Debbie Lineberger','','Open mid-April through Halloween, Open Mon-Sat; hours vary from month to month depending on crops harvested, Hours will be updated on this site, or are available on our \"Crop List.\" Note: Open Sundays ONLY in May','','','','300 Goforth Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28086','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d67ad30-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Moriah Farms','We live on a small dairy goat farm in Casar, NC, where we create our soaps with fresh creamy goat milk from our herd of registered French and American Alpine goats. No water is added, so the soaps are naturally rich in emollients and gentle moisturizers. We add food grade olive, coconut, palm and sunflower oils to make our soaps even better for your skin.   High quality essential oils are used to scent our soaps. We also make unscented soaps for people who are sensitive to fragrances or just like natural soaps. Colors occur naturally in milk soaps during the soap making process as various shades of cream to tan. We sometimes add herbs grown on our farm or sensibly gathered in our woods to add natural colors to the soap.   If you have never used goat milk soap, please give our soaps a try, we are confident you will like the rich, creamy lather and moisture created by our wonderful goat milk. We now have 3 American Alpine buck kids for sale, born April 2011..from excellent stock. ','704-538-7960 ','wardnader@gusaol.com ','Hope Ward','','','','moriahfarms on facebook ','','400 Moriah School Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28020 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d689274-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Owl\'s Eye Vineyard and Winery ','We are an exciting vineyard and winery located in the beautiful piedmont of Shelby, NC. We bring loads of experience and a wonderful new dimension of wine-making to an upcoming and exciting part of the country. We offer tours, tastings, weddings, receptions, rehearsal dinners and private events. ','704-471-9196 ','wendy@owlseyevineyard.com ','Wendy Hannah-Wright','','Thursday through Saturday 12-6pm Sunday 1-6pm Wine Down Fridays 6-9pm ','','www.owlseyevineyard.com ','','1414 Metcalf Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28150','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d69fe3c-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Proffitt Family Farms  ','Proffitt Family Farms is located in the foothills of North Carolina just 35 miles west of Charlotte. Our mission is to produce high quality food grown in a natural way. We are a local source for all natural, grass fed beef for Charlotte and the surrounding region. We provide our animals with an environment that lets them live their entire lives as nature intended, by allowing to forage exclusively on pasture.   On our farm we let the cows and pasture land sustain each other with only rain and sunshine. We never give our animals any antibiotics or hormones. We practice a low stress style of cattle management. We raise healthy, happy animals.   We have a North Carolina meat handlers license and use Mays Meats as our USDA approved and licensed processor. All of our beef is hung for 14 days to assure tenderness, and then vacuum sealed in individual packs. We sell our frozen product each weekend at farmers markets in the Charlotte, NC area, or pick ups here at our farm in Kings Mountain. Feel free to stop by the farm to check us out, or visit our website for more information. Proffitt Family Farms, Brian and Shelley Eagan, 150 Old Home Place, Kings Mountain NC 28086. (704) 739-1666 ','704-739-1666 ','brianeagan@proffittfarms.com','Brian Eagan','','Friday Farm hours from 2:00 PM until 7:00 PM and by appointment any time','','www.proffittfarms.com ','','150 Old Home Place ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28086','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6b5e6d-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Redbone Willy\'s Trading Co.  ','Nestled in the foothills of the NC South Mountains,Redbone Willy\'s offers a shopping and dining experience you will not soon forget.As you ramble around and through out the store you will find something for everyone. Relax for a while in a rocking chair or hammock while enjoying a cone of authentic Homemade ice cream or an \'ol timey glass bottled Coke from the BoneHead Cafe\'.You might enjoy taking a leisurely stroll up to the DeStarte\' Bed and Breakfast Inn which is located directly behind the store. On a cool mountain morning enjoy a hot cup of coffee as you sit by the fireplace and let yourself be enchanted by the Legend of Redbone Willy. Just sit back,relax, and enjoy all the goodness that the past has to offer.    The DeStarte\' Bed and Breakfast Inn is an excellent example of a two-story Queen Anne Victorian style home nestled amidst 85 acres of rural farmland at the base of the scenic South Mountains. The Inn offers five standard bedrooms with private/or shared baths. All baths are large and spaciious. A cabin with accommodations for two are also available. All rooms have cable TV, heat and air. All guests are served a hearty full country style breakfast each morning in the dining room or on the Veranda.    Unlike what most proclaim as \" homemade\" ice cream, Redbone Willy\'s makes on premise a true authentic homemade ice cream custard. Taking a traditional family recipe and tweaking it to perfection over thirteen months, our made-from-scratch ice cream is truly \"the creamiest and most wonderful ever made\". All of our BoneHead Cafe\' sandwiches and fixings are made fresh daily and made to order. Whether your sandwich choice be a Toluca \'Mater Melt , a Big Daddy Burger,a Crabcake Burger, or a Chicken Salad sandwich our fresh squeezed lemonade, orangeade, or Southern Sweet Tea will compliment them all. Other homemade sweet favorites worth venturing out for are Peggy\'s Red Velvet Cake and our Fried Apple Pies. ','866-538-3670 ','redbonewilly@hotmail.com','Glenda B. Miller','','Open 7 days weekly, our hours are Monday thru Saturday 10 am to 6pm and Sundays 1pm to 6pm ','','www.redbonewilly.com ','','6533 Fallston Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28090 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6c2eba-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','SMITH SALES AND SERVICE  ','','704-480-0363 ','autodocshelby@aol .com ','PAUL SMITH','','','','www.smithsalesandservice.com ','','1016 EARL RD ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28150 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6d6940-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','SonRidge Farm  ','We are a small family homestead with our enterprising homeschooled children learning many heritage crafts, some of which they teach the public in workshops and seminars. They share a love of horses, the outdoors, and a desire to \"do it themselves\" from making their own butter and cheese to crafting useful items to use on the farm.    Our farm is an ever changing collection of animals; as, at 6yrs of age, Allie set out on a quest to gather \"one of everything Under the Sun.\" We have bred dairy goats for 10yrs and currently have Saanens, LaManchas, Alpines, and Nubians.    Always intersted in fiber animals, Allie started her adventure with sheep then switched her focus to Angora Goats. She still keeps a few llamas and Alpacas for their fiber. ','(704)734-0809 ','mail@SonRidgeFarm.com ','Allie Stumbo','','By appointment ','','www.SonRidgeFarm.com ','','246 Wright Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28086','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d6e50df-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','South Mountain Boer Goat Ranch  ','We are striving to raise the finest quality of Boer goats in the state and country. We have very reasonable prices and very healthy goats.   We have five Great Pyrenees Dogs, four females and two studs. Our goal is too raise fine livestock guardians for other North Carolina Goat & sheep ranchers and also for pets. Very reasonable prices. ','704-538-9160 ','TIMBAREIT@wmconnect.com','Tim Barrett','','Normal business hours- anytime!!','','www.angelfire.com/rnb/smbgr/index.html ','','112 Navaho Drive ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28020 ','','','