rvices buildings. The number of vendors and customers has nearly doubled since the move from the downtown location.   In 2004, with the help of two (2) grants totaling $125,000 from the North Carolina Tobacco Trust Fund Commission, the farmers market is now housed in a permanent 60\' x 120\' open-air shelter with a concrete floor. The facility, constructed in 2005, provides ample parking, 20 vendors spaces, electricity and public restrooms, and is a thriving, centralized marketplace for area farmers to sell their locally grown produce to the public. ','910-840-6743 ','info@columbuscountyfarmersmarket.com','Carol Shuman','','The Market is open on Tuesday, Thursday & Saturday, 7:00 AM until 12:00 Noon, May through December','','www.columbuscountyfarmersmarket.com ','','132 Government Complex Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28472 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d749f48-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Fowler\'s Supermarket  ','We are locally, family owned and operated. We offer all the services of a big-box store, but with the friendly, courteous, and appreciative customer service.   Take a short drive in the country to your hometown grocery store. We are only a few miles from the Shallotte and Myrtle Beach areas.   We also have a full deli with freshly baked breakfast biscuits and sandwiches. We offer fried chicken, fries, sandwiches and fresh pizzas for lunch along with freshly roasted meats. ','910-653-2631 ','fowlersupermarket@centurylink.net','Gloria Fowler','','We are open Monday-Saturday 6:00am to 9:00pm Sunday 9:00am to 9:00pm Deli hours 6:00am to 2:00pm Monday-Saturday','','','','13564 Swamp Fox Hwy East ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28463 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:27','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7d75ddf2-62e8-