st parties, banquets and special events. An amphitheater is planned for entertainment. In the future, hotel and retail shops will be added. ','336-236-9463 ','info@childressvineyards.com ','Mark Friszolowski','','We anticipate a Grand Opening in the Fall of 2004, and will be open daily for tours and wine tastings. ','','www.childressvineyards.com ','','P.O. Box 847 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27293','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:28','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7dbbf101-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Clark\'s Fence Builders Inc.  ','WE SPECIALIZE IN ALL AGRICULTURE FENCING','336-399-5264 ','clarksfencebldrs@yahoo.com','Brad Clark','','','','clarksfencebldrs@yahoo.com ','','168 0ld Thomasville R.d ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27107 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:28','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7dbd2e99-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Coe Forestry & Surveying','I am a Registered Forester in NC (#649) and also a Professional Land Surveyor in NC (#3320). I have been self-employed since 1991 and enjoy helping landowners in NC with establishing their property boundaries and managing their lands for the production of timber together with the benefits of wildlife, clean air, and clean water. I can help you maximize the value of your timber and minimize both your income (from the sale of forest products)and property tax burdens.','(336) 769-4673 ','coefor@bellsouth.net ','David B. Coe (Brad)','','','','','','P.O. Box 36 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27373 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:28','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7dbe1ceb-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-ab