pes and his mom would help him process them into juices and jellies.    The muscadine and scuppernongs grown today have come a long way since then. E&N Vineyards offers eight different varieties. All of these varieties are chosen for their multipurpose characteristics. They are all good for fresh fruit, ciders, juices, jellies, jams and wine. Ranging in color from black, purple, bronze and reds. ','336-682-0264 ','ezra@yadtel.net ','Ezra and Nancy Gough','','By appointment, Call ahead to 336-682-0264 (cell) or 336-940-6176 (vineyard). ','','EandNVineyards.com ','','306 Bingham and Parks ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27006 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:28','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7ddb831f-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Hidden Creek Ranch  ','We are a family owned and operated farm with 4H kids that are dedicated to raising quality livestock for meat, show and breeding.   We raise high quality Grass Fed Beef. We have been breeding Boer goats since 1999 and are always willing to help others with their goats.   We are very active in Davie county 4H, Davie County Animal Science club and Yadkin/Davie Livestock Association. ','336-940-6199 ','tifftfarm@yadtel.net ','Tifft Family Farm','','We are always open unless we are closed ','','','','1248 Eatons Church Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27028 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:28','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7ddca6be-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','HILLTOP FARM WAGYU BEEF  ','MANY OF YOU ARE FAMILIAR WITH OUR NAME. WE HAVE BEEN RAISING OSTRICHES SINCE 1995. IT IS TIME TO EXPAND THE FARM. THE WAGYU CATTLE SEEMED TO BE THE PERFECT ADDITION. THIS BREED OF CATTLE PRODUCES A MEAT BRIMMING WITH RICH, BEEFY FLAVOR AND TENDERNESS.    A