e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Organic Bakies,LLC  ','On January 2, 2008, I was talking with a dear friend about life and what we would do if we weren\'t in the corporate world. She said she would do scrapbooking, and I said I would bake. Well, we challenged each other and said this is the year of the \"anti-ninny\"! We needed to go out and push ourselves to do those things we\'d been afraid to do in the past - to honor our dreams and really try to achieve them. As new mothers, her of a less than one month old, and me, of an 8 month old, our vow had the potential to be a lot of talk with no results. But I knew that I couldn\'t sing that song to my daughter every night and ignore my dream of making the planet a little sweeter. Hypocrites aren\'t usually positive role models!    So, after doing research on line and in my kitchen, Organic Bakies, LLC, was born. \"Organic\" because I believe that we only have one earth and one chance to leave the world a better place than we found it. I now have two daughters and want them to breathe clean air, visit National Parks and enjoy the amazing natural wonders of our beautiful planet. \"Bakies\" because the products include cookies, but are baked not cooked! I heard it on a commercial and thought it was funny and clever. The name was the brilliant idea of my supportive and loving husband who batted around a baker\'s dozen names with me until he said this one!    My company creates products that taste better than other baked goods you\'ve tried. They are better for the environment because I use certified organic, fair trade and local ingredients, and they are better for you because they have no artificial ingredients. I hope you\'ll enjoy eating Organic Bakies as much as I enjoy making them! ','919-724-6150 ','wendi@organicbakies.com','Wendi Lester','','24 x 7 online operation ','','www.organicbakies.com ','','Southpoint Area ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-0030