 may be used together or separately for handspinning, knitting, weaving and felting. These qualities make Icelandic fleece a truly premium wool.    Icelandics are a truly wonderful breed of sheep. Their fleece exceeds all expectations in the color and quality. They are easy keepers (horse owners will understand this), have dispositions and personalities as different as each member of a family, they frequently keep us laughing and are as a whole an amazing animal. We practice pasture management to minimize introducing chemicals into their environment or medication into their system. We heavily skirt our fleeces, hand removing all vegetable matter. ','3366746479','icysheep@aol.com ','Amanda Hillyard ','','','','hillyardfarms.com ','','7301 Hidden Lane Ext ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27313 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:30','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7f2de1cf-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','HOMELAND CREAMERY, LLC  ','BOWMAN DAIRY IS OWNED AND OPERATED BY CHRIS AND DAVID BOWMAN. THEY ARE THE SIXTH GENERATION ON THE FARM.    HOMELAND CREAMERY WAS BUILT TO PROCESS AND PROMOTE BOWMAN DAIRY\'S PRODUCTS. THE CREAMERY IS RUN BY DAVID AND CHRIS ALONG WITH THEIR WIVES, TERRY AND JAYNE.    THE FARM HAS TOURS AS WELL AS AN ONSITE STORE WHERE YOU CAN PURCHASE OUR PRODUCTS AND EVEN GET A SCOOP OF DELICIOUS ICE CREAM MADE FRESH AT THE CREAMERY. ','336-685-6455 ','milk@homelandcreamery.com','TERRY BOWMAN','','MONDAY THROUGH SATURDAY 9AM TO 6PM. SUMMER HOURS ARE 9AM TO 9PM THURSDAY THOUGH SATURDAY JUNE 1ST THROUGH AUGUST 31ST.','','MILK@HOMELANDCREAMERY.COM ','','6506 BOWMAN DAIRY ROAD ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27283 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:30','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7f2ebeb4-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae