al Store  ','Old Mountain General Store, located on HWY 70 & Airport Rd., Statesville, N.C., features garden grown produce (local when available) including North Carolina meats by Mays and Alexander, local honey plus N.C. canned items and flour products.    When also have a thrift store, bargain book store and airbrush studio.    Old Mountain General Store buys from the community and resales at the lowest prices possible. ','828-446-1495 ','cozzenconnection@hotmail.com ','Raymond Cozzen','','Monday thru Saturday 9am to 7pm Sunday 10am to 7pm ','','cozzenconnect.freeyellow.com/oldmountainproduce.html ','','106 Airport Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28677 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7fdc0c10-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Piedmont Farm Systems  ','','704-876-4423 ','pfs@statesville.net ','Josh Hudgins','','','','www.piedmontfarmsystems.com ','','1024 Tomlin Mill Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28625 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('7fdce65b-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Squeaky Tree Honey Farm  ','Our honey farm is located in the middle of farm country and woodlands.   In summer we take our hives up to the NC foothills and get another honey crop from the sourwood trees which the bees absolutely love - and you will too.    If you know the benefits of local, raw honey and would rather not depend on sugar for all your sweatening, call us for the best taste in North Carolina. ','704-872-0038 ','dg5boys@afo.net ','David Simonson','','8:30 AM to 5:30 PM Monday through Friday, Saturday by appointment ','','www.newwaydisplay.com/honey.htm ','','1417 Alexander Street ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f