'','919-553-0016 ','boyettefarms@embarqmail.com ','Glenn Boyette','','','','www.claytonfearfarm or www.lightsontheneuse.com ','','1620 Loop Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27527 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('800223e2-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Ronnie Moore\'s Fruits & Veggies  ','Local Family Farm business. Providing fresh fruits and vegetables in season fresh from our farm to you!Growing 10+ varieties of fresh cut herbs and cut flowers. Herbs also available potted. \"Eclipse\" super sweet cantalopes and SEEDLESS Watermelons! Don\'t forget the Beauregard Sweet potatoes along with all of our greens. Sweet Charlie Strawberries in the spring along with 5 varieties of fresh lettuce and brocolli, cabbage, and, cauliflower. LOTS MOORE!!!','919-524-1921 ','sandrmoore@msn.com ','Stephanie Moore','','Winter hours:9-4 : Spring & Summer:8-5','','','','416 Alonzo Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28366 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80038b01-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Anna\'s Fresh Garden Salsa','Anna\'s Fresh Garden Salsa was established in the summer of 2009. She had a hard time finding good fresh salsa in grocery stores and began making her own. After sharing it with her friends and family, she realized that she could make her salsa for parties and events. Since receiving several comments on how fresh and tasty the salsa was, she decided to start a business selling her fresh garden salsa.    She started a garden in her back yard to grow the vegetables. But soon the demand became too much for the small garden and she had to buy fresh vegetables from local farmers. Her business has grown faster than she has expected, but the quality of the ingredients and great customer service has not changed.    Our company is a locally grown home-based business. All the ingredients are all natural, fresh vegetables and are hand cut in our kitchen. Our company is based on the belief that our customers\' needs are of the utmost importance. Our entire team is committed to meeting those needs. As a result, a high percentage of our business is from repeat customers and referrals. We would welcome the opportunity to earn your trust and deliver you the best product in the industry. ','','annakraynor@aol.com ','Anna Raynor','','Please e-mail us your order and we will respond within the same day. ','','www.annasfreshgardensalsa.com ','','PO Box 280 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27504 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1);
INSERT INTO `farmplace` VALUES ('8004f59a-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Archer Lodge Herb Farm  ','','9195534772','alherbfarm@earthlink.net ','John & Deva King','','','','','','6224 Covered Bridge Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27527 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8007b68e-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Arrowhead Farm Dairy Goats  ','A dairy goat learning experience, we cater to small (less than 10) groups. People can milk a goat, hunt for eggs - including green eggs! - feed the chickens and greet the other critters.    Grandparents of twin boys, we both love teaching them the joys and hard work of farm life. ','919-965-9306 ','arrowheadfarmnc@aol.com','Leslie Averill','','Call ahead for an appointment. ','','','','2765 Little Divine Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27576 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80094c95-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','B & M Stables','My Philosophy on Training… The methods and training that I utilize are the result of a culmination of many different horsemen who have influenced my training style over the years. Some of these horsemen are very well known in the horse industry. However, there are also others who while not so well known, impacted my training style greatly. The experiences I gained from them led me to develop a unique program that is designed to help owners and their horses build upon their relationship in a safe and controlled manner. Whether we are building a house, or building a partnership, the need for the correct tools is no different. This program which is called the \"Seven Keys to Unlocking Performance\" are a set of tools that is used to influence and improve performance in the horse through communication rather than repetition. Each tool serves as an ingredient that assists in communication. With practice and the use of feel rather than repetition, the owner and horse begin to maneuver together and develop an understanding. In that understanding we begin to realize that as we continuously strive to improve our horsemanship, we are also broadening the training of our horses through the knowledge that we have gained.    What makes us different? § We do not profess instant training cures. Training takes time, dedication and practice. § We do not profess any \"cure all\" bits or tack. Knowledge and excellent horsemanship is the key. § Our training style is based on excellent horsemanship, empathy for the horse, and a commitment to our clients. § We do not desire fame or recognition from our services. What we do desire is for our clients to succeed in their horsemanship endeavors. ','919-934-1344 ','sileeno@ipass.net ','Blaine McLaughlin','','','','www.ipass.net/blaine_mclaughlin ','','1305C Lakewood Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27524 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('800ae164-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','BANKS MINIATURE HORSE FARM','','919-553-7216 ','BBANKS3431@AOL.COM ','BILL BANKS','','','','','','2667 PEELE ROAD ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','',' 27520 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:31','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('800bdefe-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','BANKS MINIATURE HORSE FARM  ','','919-553-7216 ','bbanks3431@aol.com ','BILL 0R PAM BANKS','','','','','','2667 PEELE ROAD ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f