ruck farming and a pack of flower seeds to plant around the house. With all those petunias we discovered a new branch of farming.    Over the years we have grown and expanded. We now grow and sell culinary herbs, Hydrangeas, and Daylilies. We also have seasonal plants including Tibouchina, Mandevilla, and Passion Vines.    We love what we do and are committed to growing and selling only what we ourselves would buy. We do not believe in the overuse of pesticides and therefore let beneficial insects do our control. ','(919) 894-4743 ','growers@herbsatbramblewood.com','Jeff Lee','','From April 1st to November 1st 9:00am- 5:00pm Seven days a week ','','www.herbsatbramblewood.com ','','366 Old Lee Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27592 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80135f02-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Brown Farm Corn Maze  ','Billy and Anne Brown, their family and staff invite you out for some great country fun. Test your sense of direction navigating through our 5.0 acre Pride in Farming maze!    We have moved the maze 2.3 miles to the Homeplace!! After a great 2002 season we were looking forward to our 2003 season. Unfortunately Mother Nature was not very nice to our First in Flight maze. Hurricane Isabel CRASHED it after being open for only two weekends.After a valiant effort from family, friends and neighbors who volunteered their time to help salvage the maze we were forced to close. But we are back and ready for you to come out and visit us at the farm!     No trip to the Maze is complete without a hayride. Take one after you finish the Big Maze to the pumpkin patch and back.The covered maze is great for the liitle ones and has slides inside the paths! Snacks, drinks restrooms and picnic area available on farm. Fall decorating stuff!!Pumpkins,straw,corn bundles and cornstalks for sale. Mums by Mom\'s Mums. ','919-550-6259 ','BRB Farms@aol.com ','Anne or Billy Brown','','Sept.17th - Nov.13th (Fri. 5-9pm Sat. 2-9pm) Oct.19th - Nov. 14th (Every Sunday 1-6pm) *SPECIAL HOURS OF OPERATION* *Oct. 22nd- Oct. 30th (*Mon.-Fri. 5-9pm) (*Sat. 2-10pm) *Oct. 31st (Sunday 1-10pm) No Sunday Haunting!(except for Halloween night Oct. 31st','','www.cornfieldmaze.com ','','399 Loop Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','',' 27520 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8014234c-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Bushrods farm','','919 868 6502 ','Bushrodsfarm@yahoo.com ','michael stancil','','','','','','hwy 50 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27504 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80156585-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Cakes Unlimited by Benisha  ','I offer delicious desserts of all sorts and at reasonable prices. All products are baked fresh and I use the best quality ingredients in all my products. All cakes are baked from my home kitchen which has been inspected and approved by the North Carolina Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services Food and Drug Protection Division.     It is my goal to make sure that my customers are completely satisfied with their order. At Cakes Unlimited by Benisha, you will get the best customer service with your order along with a moist and delicious product that you will not get off your local grocery store shelf. Grocery store cakes are mass produced and shipped frozen. They are decorated in ten minutes or less and then sat out on the shelf for consumer purchase. My cakes are given individualized attention to make your cake a work of \"customized edible art\". ','919-257-0215 ','benishanewell@cak