c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Peaceful Gardens','Welcome to Peaceful Gardens Where Butterflies and Hummingbirds Surround and Play Among the Magnificent Beauty and Aroma of Herbs and Perennials located in Franklin, North Carolina.     Future Events: Cooking With Herbs, Herbal Tea Harvesting,Harvesting Herbs and Herbs in the Bible','828 349 3024 ','darlene2@dnet.net ','Darlene Kiely','','Monday thru Saturday 9:00 to 5:00 please call before coming to Peaceful Gardens ','','www.peacefulgardensnaturally.com ','','1545 Mashburn Branch Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28734 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('807cd715-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','River Road Farm','We are a small naturally grown blueberry and blackberry farm. We use only organic chemicals and fertilizers, but are not \"certified\" organic. We are members of ASAP (Appalachian Sustainable Agriculture) and NCANA (North Carolina Agritourism Networking Association).     Nestled in the mountains of Western North Carolina, between Franklin and Highlands, we are part of the local food movement, providing great products in a location that is easy to find. We pride ourselves on having a U-Pick operation that is easily accessible and clean. We keep the rows mowed and the bushes trimmed for ease of picking.     For 2010, our prices are $2.00 per pound for both blackberries and blueberries. If you want to be added to our \"Berry Alert\" list with schedules and directions, just email us at: lennyjordan@gmail.com','770-330-3280 ','lennyjordan@gmail.com ','Lenny Jordan','','Monday and Wednesday 4:30-7:00pm Friday - 9:00am-1:00pm Call for other hours - 770-330-3280 ','','riverroadfarmnc.com ','','3738 River Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28734 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32'