ecipes handed down to him through generations of his family. He moved to Charlotte, NC in 1986 and opened a small cafe with a menu straight from the heart of the Caribbean. It is named for his mother, Ann, and himself, Tony. It is still located in Charlotte, NC at the corner of 7th Street and Pecan Avenue. New restaurants are now open in Charlotte at 6434 West Sugar Creek and at Mayfaire Community Center in Wilmington, NC. Franchises are being awarded for 2007.     Anntony\'s Caribbean Cafe has won many awards, received favorable reviews and accolades for it\'s innovative style and tasty Island cuisine. Rotissiere chicken marinated and seasoned for an authentic Caribbean flair has made our restaurants famous. This flavorful fare caused such a stir, Dr. Martin had to create his unique and flavorful sauces and dry spices for retail sale.     Currently Anntony\'s Enterprises, LLC sells our products in supermarkets such as Harris-Teeter and other grocers in the Southeast. We also sell to specialty distributors who deliver Anntony\'s products to many other retailers throughout the country. Our products can also be purchased on the web at www.anntonys.com. ','704-608-9031 ','tony@anntonys.com ','Tony Martin','','7:00 AM-4:30 PM, Monday through Friday, We sell wholesale only except through the web-site. ','','www.anntonys.com ','','2408 Lochstone Ct. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28210 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80a69656-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Caribe Food Development Inc.','','704-522-6160 ','cfdinc@bellsouth.net ','Dr. Tony Martin','','','','anntonys.com ','','6012-F Old Pineville Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28217 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:32','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80a754b6-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b6641