 average quarter side weighs about120 lbs. D D Farms customers say our aged Angus filets are the best steaks you\'ll ever eat! ','704-545-5583 ','caddlco@aol.com ','D D FARMS','','','','D D Farms & Vineyard ','','7663 Allen Black Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28227 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:33','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80aa2930-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Feisty Mama Salsa, LLC','','866-563-4078 ','info@feistymamasalsa.com ','Debra Dickson','','9am-2:30 and always by email at info@feistymamasalsa.com ','','www.feistymamasalsa.com ','','15105-D John J. Delaney Drive #332 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28277 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:33','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80ab1541-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','greeneman farms  ','we have our own brand and carry 15 other goodness grows in nc members products ','704-575-6473 ','sales@greenemanfarms.com','jerry greene','','on phone 7 days a week ','','www.greenemanfarms.com ','','801 e morehead st #102 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28202 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:33','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('80ac0363-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Lance, Inc. ','Lance, Inc., headquarted in Charlotte, NC, manufactures and markets snack foods throughout much of the United States and Canada. Lance has manufacturing facilities in Charlotte, North Carolina; Burlington, Iowa; Hyannis, Massachusetts as well as Guelph and Waterloo, Ontario. The Company\'s products are distributed mainly through a direct-store-delivery','800-995-2623 ','fresh@lance.com','','','','','www.lancesnacks.com ','',