is raised on an all natural diet. Our beef is naturally lean and tender, due to our growing methods and aging process.     All our beef is vacuum packed and is USDA inspected. We only process cows we raise, we would never sell you something we wouldn\'t keep ourselves.     Tasting is believing. Give us a try, we know you won\'t be disappointed. ','336 629-7152 ','tlingold57@embarqmail.com','Terry Ingold','','We are open every Wednesday from 10-6:00, All other times by appointments. ','','www.ingoldfarms.webs.com ','','784 Ross Harris Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27205 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:35','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82351e14-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Kathy\'s Sweet & Sassy BBQ Sauce','My Sauce is 17 yrs in the making. Full of a rich sweet and smokey flavor it is sure to please even the most select taste buds.     I am so excited to finally be able to offer Kathy\'s Sweet & Sassy sauce to the public. I am sure you will love it! ','336-873-7054 ','sweetandsassysauce@embarqmail.com','Kathy Moore','','Please call for times Avaliable, (336)-873-7054 ','','','','5007 Graves Country Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27341 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:35','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8236a119-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','L & E Associates ','We began bottling Big Daddy’s Marinade out of our love for cooking and entertaining our family and friends. My dad began making this marinade forty years ago when he was barbequing pigs for “pig pickin’s“. As a small child, living on our farm in eastern North Carolina, I can still remember that spicy taste of his marinade on the hot, fresh Bar-B-Que.     Over the years, my wife, Laura, and I have refined the recipe and expanded its use on all types of meat and cooking creations. We marinade fish, shrimp, chicken, and pork tenderloin then roll in a dry breader for frying. Marinade pork loin roast, and baby back ribs and slow bake until tender and juicy. When grilling chicken and steaks, there is nothing better to bring out the flavor of the meat. We also use it to season collards and cabbage. Several of our customers Big Daddy’s as the spice in their Bloody Marys. As we cooked using Big Daddy’s Marinade, our friends would ask how we got that spicy flavor. We would give them some marinade and the container would come back empty with everyone asking for more. It seemed as though they couldn’t get enough of that spicy marinade.     Big Daddy’s Marinade is a tenderizing spicy marinade which is designed to enhance the natural flavors of meats when grilling, frying, or roasting. While most marinades simply coat the meat’s surface, Big Daddy’s Marinade penetrates the meat passing flavor through the entire cut. We like it and once you try it, we know you’ll love it. ','336-688-7550 ','eric-henderson@triad.rr.com ','Eric & Laura Henderson','','','','www.bigdaddycooks.com ','','P.O. Box 4239 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27263 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:35','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8237de8f-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','SUZIE Q BBQ SAUCE INC.  ','Our family has used this recipe for 40 years.We are certain once you try this sauce, you will be hooked.','3368572890','suel@rtmc.net ','SUE LOWE','','Someone is home most all the time, Call to make sure','','','','4914 FARMER DENTON RD ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27239 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:35','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8238af69-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1