 just make sense to recycle your possessions? ','828-287-4319 ','funki_fungi@yahoo.com ','Joanne Waller','','MONDAY THRU FRIDAY 9:30 AM - 5 PM SATURDAY 10 AM - 4 PM','','','','480 S. Main St. (US 221) ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28139 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82e40bce-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','HeirloomFarms ','Heirloom\'s have taken a back seat to the Hybrids in the past few years. Now the old favorites are very sought after. The commerical farms todayneed the faster growing and longer shelf life brands of hybrids.     At Heirloom farms my wife and I plan to grow the old type veggies. Today the high end chefs demand organic grown heirlooms. ','828-286-4008 ','barneycole@att.net ','barneycole','','Open Mon.-Fri. 8:oo-4:00 Sat. 8;00-12:00 ','','','','581 baber rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28139 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82e58355-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Horn\'s Home And Garden  ','Horn\'s Home and Garden is family owned and operated and has been created by three generations of knowledgeable and enthusiastic gardeners. The store\'s warm and homey atmosphere evokes familiar feelings of a simpler bygone day. Horn\'s carries all your gardening needs from seed, fertilizer and potting soil to annuals, perennials and herbs. Featuring a large selection of silk flowers, we specialize in floral arranging and gladly take custom orders. We also carry Yankee Candle to help keep your home wonderfully fragrant through all seasons of the year. For your Christmas decor, Horn\'s has rooms filled with beautiful ornaments, garlands, wreaths, berries and ribbon. ','828-245-7505 ','grow@HornsHomeAndGarden.co