perb mothers and lamb easily without assistance. Their smaller size makes them easy to handle and ideal for acreages or small farms. Jacobs are a dual purpose breed, providing beautiful wool and lean, delicious meat. All things considered, this a breed that is truly a joy to raise! ','828-248-9533 ','perfectspot@bellsouth.net','Cathy & Greg Robinson','','By appointment only. ','','www.perfectspot-farm.com ','','176 Bronze Circle ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28043 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82e96c0c-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Possum Hollow Working Dogs  ','We raise and train working Border Collies for herding, specializing in one line of dogs for cattle and another line for sheep. We also provide lessons, demonstrations for events, and have an annual Cattle Herding Trial.     Our herding dogs are Border Collies bred from the finest bloodlines available. Our livestock guardian dogs are Anatolian Shepherds bred specifically for caring for livestock of any kind.     Please visit our website to see more about us and what we have to offer. ','828-286-8116 ','info@possumhollowfarms.com ','Vicki Hughes','','By appointment only. ','','www.possumhollowfarms.com ','','371 CC Lovelace Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28139 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82ea50b2-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Puddlefoot Stables  ','','828-288-8106 ','puddlefootstables@hotmail.com','Kimberley Olson','','','','puddlefootstables.com ','','362 Cash Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28139 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82ebb67f-62e8-11e1-