 is from cows owned, fed, cared for and milked daily on the Jackson family farm. Milk produced today is pumped directly to our plant for pasteurization and delivered to your store in less than 24 hours. No competition cam compare. Most raw milk is transported for many miles and several days before processing and packaging-its freshness and origin are unknown.     PURE FRESH products are approved for I.M.S. shipment. Our milking and processing facilities are I.M.S. rated for use and shipment anywhere in the United States. ',' 910-567-2721 ','jack@intrstar.net ','Cris A. Jackson','','6:00 A.M. to 6:00 P.M. Monday through Saturday, Closed Sunday','','','','1566 Dairy Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28334 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82f4e1cd-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Mac\'s Farms Sausage Company, Inc. ','','910-594-0095 ','macfarms@intrstar.net ','Scott McLamb','','','','','','209 Raleigh Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28366 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82f68c4b-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Michele\'s Fresh Fruit  ','We always only sell fresh produce. We guarantee our products. You are offered suggestions for selecting and handling your fruit. We also give you samples so you can taste what you are buying.     Please come by the Raleigh Farmer\'s Market and visit our stand. You will not be disappointed you did.     Our farm is located in Eagle Springs, which is in Moore County. For the year, 2007 we lost our peach crop due to freeze. It is now year 2009 and crop is doing good. We have a very good peach crop & other fruit to choose from. Come by and taste the difference growing fruit in the sandhill makes. ','910-892-7582 ','sandhillpeach38@aol.com ','Michele Core','','9am-5pm Monday thru Saturday 9am-4pm Sunday ','','','','2481 Plainview Hwy ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28334 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82f79166-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Old Hickory Barbecue, Inc.  ','Old Hickory Barbecue, Inc. was established in the mid 1950\'s. Our mission is and always has been to provide the best Barbecue Pork that can be found.     Old Hickory has a reputation of providing barbecue pork with no \"fillers\". This gives the customer the true taste of real barbecue.     Our product is made of fresh pork. Seasonings are added to give our Barbecue that delicious pig pickin\' flavor. ','910-567-2806 ','ohbbq@intrstar.net ','Sherrie Baxley','','Monday - Friday 8am-5pm ','','www.oldhickorybarbecue.com ','','8761 Fayetteville Hwy ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28344 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82fac45f-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','RD FARMS PREMIUM BEEF  ','For nearly 10 years, RD Farms Premium Beef has continually strived to produce the highest quality beef in the world.Over the years RD Farms has built a large and unique vertically integrated beef production system. Family owned and operated RD Farms has always taken pride raising its beef to be as pure and great tasting as nature intended. This tradition of quality is evident in all of our beef products-you can truly taste the difference. At RD Farms, we rely on the quality of our products and continuing innovation to remain competitive in the beef industry. One of the reasons RD Farms beef is superior to other beef marketers is because we\'re involved in production from the ranch to the table.      Our beef is from Hereford,Black Angus or Hereford/Angus cross steers, to take the full advantage of high quality yield grades, flavor, and tenderness, unsurpassed by anyone. All of our cattle are either born on the farm or purchased from a small network of producers, who raise their cattle under the direction of our guidelines. This is essential to meet the rigorous genetic requirements and demand for our products. Thease cattle are raised according to specified best practices and are fed according to the highest standards. The guiding principal here is to create a partnership between RD Farms and progressive producers, who are strongly focused on the prduction of a consistent,high quality, consumer driven product, with the strictest standards for food safety, environmental stewardship,and animal welfare. Through this program, RD Farms is able to source and age verify an increasing number of cattle each year.     One of the secrets to great beef is perfect attention to feeding practices. RD Farms is one of just a few producers in the country that produces beef from cattle fed in our own feedlot, regardless, if they were born on the farm or purchased from other producers. Since corn-fed-beef is the most flavorful,tender,and juicy beef avalible. RD Farms purchases locally grown corn to serve as a basis for our scientifically formulated rations. We mill all our own feeds under strict guidelines, and guidance of a consulting animal nutritionist. Given that we feed all our own cattle, we can provide our consumers with added assurances about the safety and quality of our beef. As part of our specialized feeding program, RD Farms test to ensure all ingredients used in our feed are free of pesticides. Futhermore, RD Farms has never fed any animal proteins. Our beef is processed at Chaudhry Halal Meats,Siler City;NC. Chaudhry Halal Meats is a family operated USDA inspected facility. Our beef is aged for 14-21 days, and then processed into kitchen ready cuts. Each cut is weighted, labeled, vacuum sealed, and flash frozen. It is 100% pure beef with no added chemicals or preservatives. All cuts are priced by unit package. The stated weights are approximate and typical for each cut. We also offer whole sides and half sides for sale as well, cut to your specificaitons. Call for pricing and availibilty. All our beef has been deboned as much as possible,vacuum sealed,and flash frozen for unlimited freezer storage time. Per capita consumption of beef in the USA is approximately 62 pounds. Therfore, a Half-Side of beef would be about a one year supply of beef for a family of two. Oder one today and enjoy! Ask us about our special promotions going on all the time. RD Farms is the only provider of HALAL processed beef located at the STATE FARMERS MARKET IN RALEIGH NC','910-249-3326 ','denning.robert@yahoo.com','ROBERT DENNING','','WE ARE OPEN THREE DAYS WEEKLY FROM 8AM TO 6 PM, WE CAN BE REACHED AT 910-249-3326 TO ASSIST YOU WITH ODERING OUR PRODUCTS, or letting you know what times in can be picked up at our on the farm outlet, or deliverd to you. ','','','','53 COTTONWOOD LN ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28366','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:36','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('82fc2de2-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Steve\'s Plants, LLC','We provide our customers with high quality vegetable plants, hanging baskets, annuals and bedding plants. We focus on growing plants that are well adapted to our climate and can handle our hot, humid summers.     You can also locate us on facebook. Just search for Steves plants, LLC. Our vision for our facebook page is to have contact with our customers. Steve will be available to answer questions about growing vegetables and flowers. Feel free to post questions, share a recipe or pictures of your plants. We\'ll also have information 