ry Basics stocks are unique in that they are shelf stable, pourable concentrates. This pourability feature provides for more accurate control in measuring and better hygiene as the concentrate is not continually re-contaminated by using a spoon or other utensil. In its undiluted form, Savory Basics is quite resistant to food spoilage due to its high solids content and water activity. Based on the feedback from our customers and industry professionals, we believe that Savory Basics stocks uphold our corporate vision of \"Convenience without Compromise\". We are committed to retain this vision as we strive to expand our product range and customer base. ','919-303-5300 ','rgreene@savorybasics.com','Bob Greene','','','','www.savorybasics.com ','','2508 Reliance Avenue ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27539  ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:38','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('83de83bc-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Sauced Pitmaster','','919-834-8350 ','amanda@empireeats.com ','Amanda Fekety','','','','','','133 Fayetteville St, 6th floor ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27601 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:38','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('83df5dcf-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Southport Seafood Company  ','We are a small fishing fleet that specializes in the absolute freshest seafood available. We pick our shrimp up direct from our boat and truck it in our trucks to the triangle area. ','919-291-3286 ','jason@southportseafoodcompany.com ','Jason Stegall','','','','www.southportseafoodcompany.com ','','709 W Johnson St Suite 202 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27603 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:38','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('