le. There is so much more that a FRS Forester can do for you. See below for a list of our services.     Timber Sale Preparation, Marketing and Administration - A FRS Forester, by following your management objectives can identify the trees to be harvested, show the woodland to potential buyers, supervise the sale and advise you on the available alternatives.    Timber Inventory and Appraisals - A FRS Forester can provide this information by performing a timber cruise and a site analysis. This involves measuring a representative sample of trees, preparing forest-type maps and calculating the volume and value of the timber. ','919-389-7855 ','dean3384@bellsouth.net ','Paul Dean','','Monday - Friday 9:00am-4:00pm ','','deanconsulting.biz/fr.html ','','7625 Roberts Rd. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27519 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:38','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('84259130-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Foster Lake & Pond Management, Inc.','Foster Lake & Pond Management, established in 1983 is fully licensed and insured. We can provide algae and aquatic weed control, fountains and aeration systems. We specialize in Year-Round lake management programs and fish stocking. We guarantee our customer friendly service.    We have over 20 years experience managing North Carolina lakes and ponds. Our expert staff can provide aquascaping, fish population analysis and enhancement. We have virtually any product you need for lake and pond enjoyment.     Learn more about us at: www.fosterlake.com or call us at 919-772-8548 in Garner or 704-344-9800 in Charlotte. ','919-772-8548 ','johnny@fosterlake.com ','Mitchell Morton','','8:00 - 5:00 Monday through Friday Other times by appointment','','www.fosterlake.com ','','183 Donmoor Ct. ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27529 ','','','','2012-0