t please call ahead for availability','','www.magnoliamanorbnb.com ','','128 Pet Burwell Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27589','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:39','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('84851a2b-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Oakville Farm','We have been in the daylily business for over 7 years. Our flowers are field grown and we do not hybridize at this time. With over 150 daylily varieties to choose from, we hope you will find the right color, size and height to fit your needs.     Daylilies are a great perennial which require 6-8 hours of sunlight per day. They tolerate most any type of soil and drought conditions. Daylilies grow from 18\" to 48\" tall and come in a full range of colors. We have early/mid/late season bloomers as well as rebloomers. Some daylilies bloom until frost.     We ship Mondays and Tuesdays to assure freshness to you. ','252-257-4454 ','xoff@earthlink.net ','Sherman Wright','','Our peak bloom season is mid June thru mid July, We are open on weekends from 8 AM til 6 PM, Please call ahead @ 252-257-4454 for special appointment. ','','www.oakvillefarm.com ','','1122 Wise-Five Forks Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27551 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:39','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('848678f9-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Roanoke Tar Forestry and Realty, Inc ','','252-532-9885 ','jdwolgemuth@earthlink.net','Jeff Wolgemuth','','','','www.roanoketarguide.com ','','PO Box 27 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27584 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:39','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8487fb93-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5