present to bring our customers precise portion control, which allows the freedom to create without the hassle of slicing and trimming. ','800-828-4934 ','billgoodnight@bellsouth.net ','Bill Goodnight','','8am - 5pm','','www.goodnightbrothers.com ','','372 Industrial Park Drive ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28607 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:39','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8490d6c4-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Hospitality Mints','Hospitality is Our Business. It’s in our name, and it’s always in everything we do from outstanding service and dedication to our customers and an efficient distribution process to the friendly people who are part of the Hospitality Mints team. At Hospitality Mints, our promise to you is hospitality wrapped up in our distinctive, mouthwatering candies that come with an array of customized wrappers and packaging options to convey your perfect message of hospitality. We create warm, friendly ways to promote your company, say thank you or give a welcome and memorable gift.      We produce 4 million hard and soft candies a day in 23 taste-tempting varieties at state-of-the-art manufacturing facilities. Utilizing the latest technology and best custom processes, Hospitality Mints takes care of 4,000 customers whose needs range from one case of 1,000 candies to thousands of cases. We’ve been making delicious, creative ways for you to show hospitality for nearly 30 years in North Carolina.      Hospitality Mints maintains the highest level of hygiene throughout the candy-making and wrapping processes. For this key aspect of our manufacturing process, the American Institute of Baking has awarded a Superior rating to our company for eight consecut ','828-264-3045 ','dyates@hospitalitymints.com ','Kathi Guy','','8:00 am - 5:00 pm M-F','','www.hospitalitymints.com ','','213 Candy Lane ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11