ere at Brad\'s Blueberries.     When you come to visit, make sure to ask about our delicious blueberry recipes that passed the Brad\'s Blueberries Taste Test! ','336-766-6363 ','bradsblueberries@triad.rr.com ','Brad & Jackie','','Wednesday, Friday, Saturday: 8am - 2pm ','','http://www.ncagr.gov/ncproducts/ShowSite.asp?ID=100290 ','','3108 Old Hwy. 421 East ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27055 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('850ebd3d-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Creek Side Farm','','336-835-4480 ','adickerson7@earthlink.net ','Perry, Alesia or Michael Dickerson','','','','','','3313 Swan Creek Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','28642 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('85103f9f-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Flint Hill Vineyards ','Flint Hill Vineyards is located on land that has been in the family for over 130 years, thereby designated as a Century Family Farm from the USDA. We planted our vineyard about 8 years ago and house our tasting room and newly opened Fine Dining Restaurant, Century Kitchen, in the old 1870\'s style farmhouse that the family grew up in. In August of 2007 we opened, Century Kitchen, a casual fine dining restaurant, dedicated to providing as local and fresh food as we can. The menu can be found on our website flinthillcenturykitchen.com. We serve lunch every Friday, Saturday and Sunday from 12 to 4 and dinner Thursday thru Saturday from 5 to 9:30 pm. We also have a larger brunch on the 1st sunday of every month from 11:30 to 4 pm. Call 336-699-4455 for reservations or online through our website.     The property is surrounded by century old oak trees, perfect for a picnic lunch or a glass of wine. Come visit us for a relaxing country experience you will never forget. ','336-699-4455 ','fhvineyards@yadtel.net ','Brenda Doub','','Tasting room is open Thursday thru Sunday from 12 to 5 pm, All wines can be purchased during restaurant hours as well.','','www.flinthillvineyards.com ','','2153 Flint Hill Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27018 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('851114eb-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Four Ladies and Me Farm  ','We are a family farm specializing in show and pet quality llama for sale. We also have a vineyard and wine tasting room opening to the public in the Spring of 2009. We currently have a few miniature horses for sale also. Farm tours, birthday parties and summer camps are available.','336-972-7625 ','mwest5133@aol.com ','Michael West','','','','www.fourladiesandme.com ','','5351 Macedonia Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27055 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('851299cf-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Green Mesa Blueberry Farm  ','The Green Mesa Blueberry Farm was established in 2002.We have two acres of blueberries with five different varieties to choose from. These delicious berries range from sweet to tangy.     You can enjoy the country atmosphere while you pick,with cattle grazing and other farm crops growing nearby. We are conveniently located and easy to find.     You may call ahead and place your order. We will be glad to pick for you. ','336-468-8878 ','greenmesa@yadtel.net ','Arlene Frazier','','Monday, Wednesday - Saturday, 8am - 5pm, weather and field conditions permiting, You may call ahead, We expect to begin picking mid-June. ','','','','3532 Baptist Ch. Rd. ','7