g in the woodsa€|get grounded...and back in touch with nature. Hemric Century Farm is great place for long walks; thinking, planning or just relaxing or taking in area events. Gather together your positive energies and enjoy your surroundings. Veta Hemric is a Master Hypnotist; skilled in yoga, guided imagery and creative visualization. Hemric Century Farm is creative visualization. You are encouraged to schedule wellness and other educational and fun retreats; 1, 2 and 3 day stays are available; get a new lease on life; morning walks, and yoga too. Our retreats and shade making classes are funa€|     Event & Festival grounds: Greenbrier Place is sponsoring its inaugural RamKat Run & Walk 5k on July 12, 2008. Register now to be part of this our first time event. Ramfest features Arts, Crafts, Literary, Wellness Presentations and Music On The Green from 4-8pm...July 12 kicks off the first of many such annual events. This party starts at 9:00 am sharp on July 12, with RamFest vendors ready for you. The RamKat Run & Walk 5k starts promptly at 9:00. Register NOW! The invitation is out for sharing your NC talents, products and/or NC produce. RamFest: Reserve your ffordable vendor booth(s)..plan to enjoy your escape to the country for Fun, Family, Food, & Festivities to benefit the Hemric Century Farm Preservation Fund. Bring a blanket or lawn chair for Music on the Green 4-8 p.m. Rock, country & western & more ... something for everyone. The 1929 barn turns into the NUT House and features NC Peanuts for RamFest.Vendor booths and Tickets on sale now info line: 334-244-7556 or 800-263-2563 ext. 5267     Garden & Woodland Weddings. Make plans to showcase your wedding and its associated social events at either Greenbrier Place or Hemric House. We feature Greenbrier Place Weddings and Weddings Off Meadowbrook. Showers, teas, luncheons and more....catered on-site social gatherings, by the pool is great.','336-244-7556 ','VetaHemric@gmail.com ','Veta Hemric ','','We are open by