01b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27020 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('8519afdd-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Hutchens Farm  ','Hutchens Farm if a small Family Owned and Operated Cattle and Hay farm located in East Bend, NC. We take pride is raising beef to be as pure and great tasting as nature intended. Our herd consist of Registered and commercial Polled Hereford and Black Angus. Our cattle is free of growth hormones, steriods and antibiotics. They eat either fresh pasture growth or with stored grasses such as hay or hay silage and are only given enough grain to keep them calm and gentle. Ours calves are allowed to grow at a natural rate. Each cattle will be raised solely on grass to insure a natural taste and texture to your meat when slaughter time comes.      Our beef is slaughtered and processed at a NCDA inspected facility. The meat is dry aged for flavor and tenderness, then cut to your specifications. Grass fed beef has a rich flavor and texture, is higher in Omega 3 fatty acids than commercial products, while being much leaner over all. It is reported that these acids aid the human immune system in fighting diabetes, arteriosclerosis, and cancer.      The hay variety that we sell is Orchard grass, Fescue and Alfalfa. We also sell small bales of straw. ','336-961-2708 ','whutchens@yadtel.net ','Wade Hutchens, Jr.','','By appointment only-call anytime. ','','','','1845 Falcon Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27018 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('851b32c0-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Laurel Gray Vineyards  ','Our family came to the Yadkin Valley of North Carolina from London, England in 1773 and for 10 generations have remained. Visit our restored circa 1930\'s milking parlor, taste our award winning estate wines and become our new friends.     Currently our vineyards consist of Chardonnay, Cabernet Sauvignon, Viognier, Syrah, Cabernet Franc and Merlot. Laurel Gray is family owned and operated, therefore we give our grapes tender loving care.     Located in the beautiful foothills of the western Piedmont of North Carolina, Laurel Gray Vineyards is an easy one hour dirve from Greensboro, Charlotte, Virginia or Boone. ','336 468-8463 ','laurelgray@yadtel.net ','Kim Myers','','Wednesday 1:00pm - 6:00pm, Thursday and Friday 10:00 am - 6:00pm, Saturday 10:00am- 5:00pm, Sunday 1:00pm - 5:00pm ','','www.laurelgray.com ','','5726 Old US Hwy 421 ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27020 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('851c00a1-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Loflin Handle Co., Inc.','Visit Our Web Page At www.yadkinhandle.com ',' 336.463.2422 ','lhcinc@yadtel.net ','J.H. Loflin, Jr.','','8a.m. to 5 p.m. Monday through Friday','','www.yadkinhandle.com ','','2625 Courtney-Huntsville Road ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-11e0-b192-00306701b527','','27055 ','','','','2012-02-29 15:17:40','a1c3e20e-f181-11e0-8a53-00306701b527',1),('851d76c9-62e8-11e1-b30d-101f74b66417','ff2b0b4d-203c-11e1-8a87-000c29a5c50c','','06a017ae-28cb-11e1-abb7-000c29a5c50c','Riley Livestock, INC ','Our goal is to provide the consumers in North Carolina with access to quality Hogs at competitive prices.     Hogs are available every Saturday 9-12. All Hogs Will be bought and sold by the pound.     We also buy hogs, cattle, sheep, and goats. Pricing will be available on the Friday before. ','336-477-5165 ','rileylivestock@yadtel.net ','Zane Riley','','Saturday 9-12.','','','','3729 Westwood Rd ','7f7a92b8-ea4c-11e0-8606-00306701b527','ed336e0f-f48c-